  "prompt": "Does Toptal ever do any discounts?",
  "response": "Toptal, a platform known for connecting businesses with top freelance talent, rarely offers discounts due to its premium service model. However, there have been occasional promotions and special offers in the past. Here are a few points to consider:\n\n1. **Referral Program**: Toptal has a referral program where both the referrer and the referee can receive benefits, such as credits or discounts on future services.\n\n2. **Enterprise Discounts**: Larger enterprises or those committing to long-term engagements may be able to negotiate custom pricing or volume discounts.\n\n3. **Promotional Periods**: Keep an eye on Toptal's official communications, such as newsletters or social media, as they may announce special promotions during certain times of the year or for specific services.\n\n4. **Trial Periods**: While not a traditional discount, Toptal sometimes offers a trial period where you can test their services at a reduced rate or with certain guarantees.\n\nTo get the most current information, it's best to directly contact Toptal's sales team or check their official website for any ongoing promotions or special offers.",
